{12.30p.m.}Play outside on the playground and field.{1.15p.m.}In time and register.{1.30p.m.}Maths.{ {2.15p.m.}Reading.{2.45p.m.} P.E.(Physical Education){3.15p.m.}Pack away and tidy up.{3.20p.m.}Drama club. {4.15p.m.}Go home{4.25p.m.}Have a drink and watch television.{4.45p.m.}Play on my bike.{5.00p.m.}Teatime.{5.30p.m.} Play down at the playing field at Wreake Crescent with Alice and Sarah Jayne.{7.30p.m.}Watch television{ {8.00p.m.}Bedtime and read in bed.{ {9.00p.m.}Fall asleep.
*The end of the afternoon/evening on Tuesday 1st. October 1985*
